content:
Einstein Discovery allows you to impute missing text values in your dataset. Enable imputation on a text variable, and Einstein Discovery automatically replaces missing values with data derived from another subset of your data.

Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Also available in Developer Edition, CRM Analytics (for an extra cost) in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

In Model Setup, select a variable that contains Replace Missing Values alert to open its Settings. Click the Transform dropdown menu and select Replace Missing Values. Click Update Model. Return to review the predicted values in the table and chart.
title: Imputing Missing Text Values with Einstein Discovery
